    </div>
    <div class="how-step reveal">
      <div class="how-num">2</div>
      <div class="how-title">Log expenses</div>
      <div class="how-body">Add expenses as they happen — who paid, who was involved, the amount and a category.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-step reveal">
      <div class="how-num">3</div>
      <div class="how-title">Settle up</div>
